fr.n7.saceca.u3du.model.graphics.animation
Class Animation

java.lang.Object
  fr.n7.saceca.u3du.model.graphics.animation.Animation
Direct Known Subclasses:
AppearAnimation, ChangeTrafficLightAnimation, DieAnimation, DisappearAnimation, MoveAnimation, ReviveAnimation
public abstract class Animation
extends java.lang.Object

The Class Animation. It is used to :

  • send the Graphics the order to execute this animation.
  • send the animation back to the IA (with a result) when the Graphics estimates the animation is finished.

Author:
Aurélien Chabot & Jérôme Dalbert
